Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:53.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}このあたりイチバン見晴らしの良いあの木に登って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:01.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}あの子が笑う 無邪気に笑う 夢を見る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:25.56,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}空を泳いだ魚の向こうじっと目を凝らせば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:32.57,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}町の隅っこ色褪せてゆく日々がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.78,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ゆびきりしたままで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.74,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}サヨナラしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:48.75,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}果たされる日を待ってこの木に宿るよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何回も繰り返す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:57.01,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そのたび涙する
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}止まって動き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.02,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}そのすべてを確かめるように
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:13.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ほら やまびこが聞こえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:53.49,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}爬上這一帶視野最美的那棵樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:01:01.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}孩子笑了 笑得天真無邪 她看到了夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.68,0:01:25.56,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}定定地盯著空中暢遊的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:32.57,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}小鎮每個角落裡漸漸褪色的日子浮現出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.82,0:01:36.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}打勾勾上吊百年不變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:39.74,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}即使分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:48.75,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}等待約定實現的心情也寄託在這棵樹上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:52.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}一遍一遍地重複
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:57.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}每次都止不住淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:02:00.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}停下來又繼續走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿是要印證這一切似的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.14,0:02:13.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}山間回音響不絕 妳說是不是呢
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,===========Story================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.81,0:00:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要抓一大堆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.82,0:00:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼螺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:13.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田螺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是田螺呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.28,0:00:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡有好多呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.83,0:00:22.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 收集到大量豐年蝦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.29,0:00:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到蝌蚪蝦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:43.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到一大堆
Comment: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:18.49,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1135.066,561.866)}{\c&H4BB4F0&}來做晴天娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢螢 喜歡蝌蚪蝦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到 很稀奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.59,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次照顧它們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大家輪班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是完全由我負責
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很喜歡蝌蚪蝦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在下雨呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 今天忘記帶雨傘了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海 遮我一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:53.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那…學姊 要不我來幫妳撐傘到到巴士站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 嗯 那拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才要請學姊多多指教呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅雨季快點結束就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨也不錯呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明明天是星期天呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.76,0:03:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望明天是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車要送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.22,0:03:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買給妳了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶寄過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然有點遲 是入學賀禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.36,0:03:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣大家就能一起騎自行車去玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:47.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先不要自己一個人騎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要找人陪著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等雨停了就練習一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要練習
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來不會停的樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎不了自行車了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:28.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 做好晴天娃娃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過總感覺和我想像中的不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼小一個 太陽公公不會找到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮對晴天娃娃也很認真呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到好辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:43.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有紙碟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像餐具櫃的抽屜裡面有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:54.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.60,0:04:55.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要用來做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在紙碟上開條縫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:05:01.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用畫筆沿著線塗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在這裡纏上橡皮筋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 之前買的白色雨衣還在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在玄關喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽公公
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我成為了晴天娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姊姊 我做得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這樣出去走一圈可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還在下雨 還是不要去了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是要出去 認認真真祈求太陽公公快點出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祈求晴天是晴天娃娃的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那… 只能在我們家附近喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路小心喔
Comment: 0,0:06:05.13,0:06:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,----れんげ----
