Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}カエルは大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}おたまは子ども
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}後ろ足生えたらすねかじり
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\fs55}{\fad(200,200)\an9}*すねかじり=脛齧り
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}前足生えたら反抗期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}カエル、カエル
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}青蛙呀青蛙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}青蛙是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:15.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}蝌蚪是孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}後腿出來啃老族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:22.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}前腿出來叛逆期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HF09422&}{\an7\fs55}{\fad(200,200)}青蛙呀青蛙
Comment: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,----End----
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨天挖土好容易呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:38.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要造座山 再做條河
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.22,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輸給小鏟子的誘惑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.80,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 用這個鏟子敲水桶發出聲音的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽公公會更容易發現我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽爺爺 太陽公公 快出來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼也不停呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話看來要變成持久戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.93,0:07:38.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣沾上黑色了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 不好好工作不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 把蓮華忘記拿的漫畫送回去的路上 突然就下起雨來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.57,0:07:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有帶雨傘就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喵呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像聽到了什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是具嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在流黑眼淚和黑口水嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪嗎 這大白天的都會出現嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算是妖怪也有好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許能放過我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然離很遠看不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它拿著什麼武器
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎怎怎怎怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然拿著武器那肯定是壞妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:11.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去蓮華家找穗姊幫忙的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:16.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:18.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓準時機…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小小鞠呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來和我一起祈求天晴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一邊說著什麼一邊揮著武器追過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.09,0:09:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刺激了它的鬥爭心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨越下越大了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該去接小蓮回來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:45.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了 蓮華的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穗姊 救命 外面有妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救救救命呀 天照大神如來佛祖太陽公公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:24.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 不是壞妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.52,0:10:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想著我也變成晴天娃娃的話小蓮會高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小鞠害怕得哭了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒有哭呢 那是雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天放晴了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晴天娃娃的效果出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要練習騎自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.16,0:10:43.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也來陪妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日記 日記 日記記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該吃飯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 回去了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.91,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我要寫觀察日記
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對喔 小蓮是蝌蚪蝦負責人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 蝌蚪蝦有長大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻吃了很多飼料
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有 這隻游泳很快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有起名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫做小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪隻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:42.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們兩個快點 巴士要來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的學也上完了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.66,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得出太陽了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了晴天娃娃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.58,0:12:14.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起就害怕 拜託別再說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那個星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:21.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮打扮成晴天娃娃的樣子在外面走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了晴天努力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.89,0:12:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太努力了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:27.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.22,0:12:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去賣點心的那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去吧 剛好帶零用錢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:34.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可以去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騎自行車去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳會騎了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這聲音好懷念呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.20,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖果拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.03,0:12:47.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,賣點心的也做晴天娃娃了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨太無聊了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然做到一半雨就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,買什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種花叫做紫斑風鈴草喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紫斑風鈴草嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:22.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢袋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是屬於螢的花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an7\fs48}*紫斑風鈴草日語為ホタルブクロ，日語漢字寫做{\fnDFPPOPMix-W5}「蛍袋」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.95,0:13:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 吃晚餐了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.34,0:14:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去賣點心的那了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃飯的時候不要說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:51.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好睏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中午才開始上學就好了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 說了不要拉我衣服了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢做完作業了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做完了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:02.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海有做作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:04.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 我有帶作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.47,0:15:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:17.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然好可憐 不過也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.20,0:15:39.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蝌蚪蝦好像壽命很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華 下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.59,0:15:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回教室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.76,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水缸之後再收拾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 打開習題本
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也下課了下課了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.80,0:16:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨不停呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮 走了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天星期天 大家再一起出去玩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢 玩什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小蓮想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.97,0:17:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.81,0:17:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 巴士要來了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.61,0:17:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏海學姊沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:40.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴士來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.21,0:17:48.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.83,0:17:50.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人遲了一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 小心點呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是田地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.73,0:18:13.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對啦 明天天晴的話要不要去抓蝌蚪蝦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.90,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了很不開心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近好像開了家便利商店 要不要去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像要走兩小時左右
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 那不是很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 也就那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓮華也去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就明天下午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}小平先生去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太扯了 昨天的便利商店遠足太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 還在說那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太遺憾了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便利商店還會關門開什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是24小時營業呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.83,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明都收拾好了 為什麼水缸還在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再靠近點看看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼在裡面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是生出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我之前在想 蝌蚪蝦會不會產卵了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.19,0:20:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是就把養蝦的土放回去再加好水了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是小平先生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對 是小平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.69,0:21:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏夏 夏夏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(0,400)}小平先生出生了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好多小平先生
